  <h2>2. The service</h2>
  <p>
    PoolPilot is a native app that displays readings from your pool controller (ProCon.IP or Violet)
    and — as part of PoolPilot&nbsp;Pro — can control switch functions, dosing, the cover and setpoints.
    Communication happens directly on your local network. Reading values is free; write actions require
    an active Pro subscription or a running free trial.
  </p>

