    PoolPilot is an independent project and is not affiliated with Pool Digital GmbH. “ProCon.IP” and
    “Violet” are trademarks of their respective owners and are used only to describe compatibility.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Subscription, free trial and cancellation</h2>
  <p>
    PoolPilot&nbsp;Pro is offered as a subscription (monthly or yearly). A one-time free trial starts on
    your first successful connection to your controller; no payment details are required during the
    trial.
  </p>
  <p>
    A subscription renews automatically at the then-current price unless cancelled at least 24&nbsp;hours
    before the end of the current period. You manage and cancel it in the subscription settings of your
    App Store or Google Play account. Current prices are shown in the app's purchase dialog and on the
    app pages.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Requirements</h2>
  <p>
    To use the app you need a compatible controller, a device with a supported operating system, and a
    network over which the app and controller can reach each other. You are responsible for the setup.
  </p>

